Package: outlieR
Title: Automatic Outlier Detection Using Isolation Forests
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabian", "Distler", , "bully-jolt-cabana@duck.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides automated outlier detection in tabular data using
    isolation forests (isotree package). Features include automatic
    hyperparameter tuning, detailed per-feature outlier analysis,
    comprehensive diagnostics, and rich visualizations. Designed with a
    simple, intuitive API following data.table design principles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/fabiandistler/outlieR
BugReports: https://github.com/fabiandistler/outlieR/issues
